Director’s Cut – ‘Stay Out There’​ 
 
You love it. You hate it.  
When you’re just fully in it, ​that feeling is pretty addicting.​ 
 
Running is weird. ​ 
Running sucks more often than it feels good. ​ 
But to know, yeah it does really suck. ​ 
 ​ 
Early in the morning like that. ​ 
It just feels raw. ​ 
I always come back feeling so much better. ​ 
 
The end goal or the end result: it always feels better. ​ 
Like that accomplishment. ​ 
 
Stay Out There™
